messages.title: At the General Election, you will make a big choice about the future you want for Britain's public services.
Only Labour can beat the Tories
messages.content: A vote for the Lib Dems or any other party will let the Tories win.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Labour guarantees that you will see a cancer specialist within two weeks of GP referral. The NHS now has 89,000 more nurses and 44,000 more doctors than in 1997.
Over three-quarters of GP practices now offer extended opening hours.

quotes.text: My admiration for Thatcher, by Clegg
